<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>About Gamix Electronics</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css" />
</head>
<body>

  <!-- Logo Header -->
  <div class="shadedBorder">
    <img src="/images/Web_Logo.png" width="20%" alt="Gamix Electronics Logo">
  </div>

  <!-- Navbar -->
  <%- include('../partials/_navbar.ejs') %>

  <!-- About Content -->
  <div class="shadedBorder" style="padding: 30px; margin-top: 20px;">

    <h1>About Gamix Electronics</h1>

    <p style="line-height: 1.7; margin-top: 15px;">
      <strong>Gamix Electronics</strong> is a gaming-focused electronics store designed
      for enthusiasts who demand performance, quality, and cutting-edge technology.
      Our platform allows users to browse, manage, and explore a curated selection
      of gaming laptops and hardware.
    </p>

    <p style="line-height: 1.7; margin-top: 15px;">
      This application was built as a full-stack MEN (MongoDB, Express, Node.js) project
      featuring full CRUD functionality, user authentication, and authorization.
      Registered users can create, edit, and delete their own products while
      maintaining secure access control.
    </p>

    <p style="line-height: 1.7; margin-top: 15px;">
      Gamix Electronics emphasizes a clean UI, responsive layout, and a futuristic
      gaming theme to provide a smooth and enjoyable user experience across all devices.
    </p>

    <h2 style="margin-top: 30px;">Technologies Used</h2>
    <ul style="margin-top: 10px; line-height: 1.7;">
      <li>Node.js & Express</li>
      <li>MongoDB & Mongoose</li>
      <li>EJS Templating</li>
      <li>Session-based Authentication</li>
      <li>HTML, CSS (Flexbox & Grid)</li>
    </ul>

    <div style="margin-top: 30px;">
      <a href="/" style="text-decoration: none;">
        <button>Back to Home</button>
      </a>
    </div>

  </div>

</body>
</html>
